Fork-a-Wiki is a Markdown-based Wiki built on ConceptJS. Check out the [GitHub repo](https://github.com/conceptjs/fork-a-wiki/) for install instructions. 

The formatting is done using the [markdown-js](https://github.com/evilstreak/markdown-js) project. Check out the [Quick Markdown Example] to view the formatting options. 

Pages in this repository can be referenced as `[PageName]`. Pages in other repositories can be referenced with their http URL. You can click on a [New Page] link to create that page.
